      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a masterfully preserved vehicle in impeccable showroom condition. This unit has been maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence, retaining its original luster and mechanical precision. Every detail reflects a commitment to preservation, offering the discerning buyer an experience indistinguishable from new. This is an investment-grade acquisition for those who demand uncompromising quality.",
